KRISP extension 2.0.0

$Id: README,v 1.2 2010-07-05 09:59:55 oops Exp $


DESCRIPTION

This is python extension that is libkrisp python frontend.
This modules is thread safe.


INSTALLATION

To install this extension type the following:

    python setup.py build
    python setup.py install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these libraries:

    Over libkrisp 3.0.0

    If you use libkrisp under 3.0 (for example 2.x.x), use
    v1 branch. Head branch is required over libkrisp 3.0.0.


